derivation: from H7096 (קָצָה) in the sense of determining;
outline:
1. chief, ruler, commander
    1. chief, commander (in war)
    2. dictator
    3. ruler (of one in authority)
kjv_def: captain, guide, prince, ruler. Compare H6278 (עֵת קָצִין).
strongs_def: a magistrate (as deciding) or other leader
